data.description: Don't miss this beautifully updated and maintained home with 1,588 finished sq. ft. Newer windows, shingles, vinyl siding, additional attic insulation, concrete driveway, LVT and LVP, oak cabinetry, new front and back door with high-end screen doors, new walk in shower in main level bathroom, countertops, light and plumbing fixtures with the original oak flooring adding charm and low maintenance. Spacious finished lower level family room. Enjoy the lower level fourth bedroom featuring a large walk in closet and nearby full bath. Newer high efficiency furnace and AC. Lovely back yard with concrete patio and oversized two stall garage. Close to Noelridge Park, Wright School, I-380 and shopping.  All of the major components and then some are taken care of allowing you to move in and enjoy your new home!
